Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突擊開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕爾斯歷317年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:48.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,120)}{\fad(1200,800)}馬爾亞姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:48.11,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(951,596)}{\fad(1200,800)}帕爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面對入侵了友邦馬爾亞姆的魯西達尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕爾斯在國王安德拉寇拉斯三世的率領下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以30萬大軍進行迎擊並獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓魯西達尼亞兵的屍骸堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 再練一組
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 上部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 中部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 上部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 下部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 上部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好過分啊 巴夫利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用那種招式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種程度的東西還稱不上招式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是劍的基本動作而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果不把基本功鍛煉好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招式就會失去威力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請好好磨練基本功吧 亞爾斯蘭殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:21.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1050,0)}{\pos(246,100)}帕爾斯國 王太子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.62,0:03:21.54,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1050,0)}{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}亞爾斯蘭殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊 為什麼巴夫利斯沒有陪同父王遠征呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此地 王都葉克巴達的守衛是本次我得到的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅西方的魯西達尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:40.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1050,650)}{\pos(246,100)}帕爾斯國 大將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:40.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1050,650)}{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}巴夫利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連東方各國也都覬覦著這座首都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以萬萬大意不得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你這麼忙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何必每天來陪我練劍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這種毫無霸氣的話掛在嘴邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是無法成為出色的王者的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便只是練成了劍術基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便能夠勤其身勵其行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且殿下還未經歷初陣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了那天的到來 也必須好好鍛煉劍術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白啦 雖然明白..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.82,0:04:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然您明白 就拿出精神勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵們都在等著您呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大義在此 期待你們對帕爾斯永遠的忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:40.53,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1050,650)}{\pos(246,100)}帕爾斯國 王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:40.53,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1050,650)}{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}泰巴美娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向王妃大人以及亞爾斯蘭殿下敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？亞爾斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不..非常抱歉讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 聽說你每天都在進行劍術的練習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了成為像父王那樣出色的國王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是有在奮發圖強啦..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過總是難有長進啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是被巴夫利斯..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為出色的王者..到底是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告死天使 告命天使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 它們回來也就意味著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 告死天使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴夫利斯大人也別來無恙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇斯瓦特 你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然比飼主先跑來跟殿下打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是臭屁的傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被它們小看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:14.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,650)}{\pos(246,100)}帕爾斯國 萬騎長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:14.92,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,650)}{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}奇斯瓦特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 不能說我被小看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是它們從心底裡仰慕著殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛禽走獸是映襯人心的鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們深知殿下心靈的健康純凈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠征辛苦了 大家都沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 本方的損害十分輕微
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們帕爾斯軍成功擊退了侵入友邦馬爾亞姆的魯西達尼亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德拉寇拉斯陛下凱旋歸來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.83,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,0)}{\pos(246,100)}帕爾斯國 第十八代國王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.83,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,0)}{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}安德拉寇拉斯三世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:04.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,650)}{\pos(246,100)}帕爾斯國 萬騎長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:04.30,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,650)}{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}卡蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬騎長 卡蘭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蘭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:09.68,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,650)}{\pos(246,100)}帕爾斯國 萬騎長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:09.68,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,650)}{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}克巴多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊那位是馬魯斯潘·克巴多大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在喝著酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人有清醒的時候嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他左眼的那道傷痕 是和龍戰鬥時留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是最喜歡雙刀將軍奇斯瓦特大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長大之後我也要加入騎兵隊 去保護國王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 國王大人哪需要護衛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家13歲就打倒了獅子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是魯西達尼亞兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是所謂的“為神而戰”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依亞爾達波特教麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說只要是異教徒 就算嬰孩也要趕盡殺絕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太野蠻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是個孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連那樣的小孩都抓來上戰場啊 魯西達尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的父母到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父王 您平安無事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在遠方戰鬥實在令人擔心..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴夫利斯 來報告留守期間的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞爾斯蘭王子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 靠不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我們的保護才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要年輕人 要能幹體力活的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子 跑來這種地方實在有些..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得有機會和魯西達尼亞人交談啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果需要奴隸的話 讓下人去辦就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我想親自打聽打聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面的國家的情況 外面的人們的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋 給我乖乖聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是亞爾斯蘭殿下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎能來這等煩悶之地呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些人就是魯西達尼亞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話 我想和你們聊一聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 看你幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們已經是奴隸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想活命就給我聽話 聽明白沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 還是別幹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦 到現在還說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要加入騎兵隊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能這麼膽小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓他不敢違抗我們帕爾斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狠狠教訓他一頓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些個野蠻人 要是王子有什麼閃失就追悔莫及的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒那麼笨 會小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子 請留步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心我宰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊 能否放了此子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是麼..那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等..痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商品逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..如果只是逃走還好說..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子他 為了保護我們..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我搜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事這麼吵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達龍大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞爾斯蘭王子他！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(246,100)}帕爾斯國 萬騎長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:27.32,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}達龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 快追
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放開那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢靠近我就把這傢夥的脖子給折了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死的話就跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起來 蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞爾斯蘭王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這種事傳到宮裡的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 他們往哪跑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用這麼大的陣仗來追
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢夥 是個大戶人家的少爺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把人質換成你 看來做對了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 幫大忙了..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個長脖子生物是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒見過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戲班子經常帶來表演的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這一帶的生物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多麼富饒的國度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處都是物資和人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟這裡是大陸公路的中心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕爾斯人不愁吃穿 過著富饒文明的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別廢話 給我上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隸倒是不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大量的奴隸是這個國家富強的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你要逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖當個奴隸的話 就不愁吃喝了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少比起魯西達尼亞的生活要來得好吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼 你是說我的國家很貧窮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不啦 因為連你這樣的小孩都被派來戰鬥..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是小孩子 我已經11歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11？和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了這個年紀就已經是堂堂戰士了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們對依亞爾達波特神效忠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勢必要將異教徒斬盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要這麼痛恨異教徒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的神平等待人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你們又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把人踐踏在他人腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個奴隸制度是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的神容不得這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你們這些不服從我神教誨的異教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通通殺光也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,語無倫次啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢夥..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 還來？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要所有人都信仰依亞爾達波特神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紛爭根本就不會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你是在無憂無慮中成長的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不諳世事的小少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想看看你爸媽長什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下邊好像很慌亂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 泰巴美娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的這段期間 別來無恙吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少把盔甲脫了如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了一些上好的綢子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是麼 請放在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在西邊的城墻 別讓他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不管這個人死活了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投降吧 別白白送死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達龍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.77,0:17:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從上面掉下來的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使勁 好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷馬賊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達龍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.10,0:18:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達龍 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞爾斯蘭殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您沒受傷吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,達龍 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:43.24,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的馬啊 快抓回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:44.93,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 你先冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼您要阻止我射死他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..自然而然就..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 就當我射偏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事就太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說被俘虜抓著滿城跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您務必再小心一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是稍有不慎您剛才就沒命了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經你這麼一說..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王太子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,導致俘虜逃脫的三人已經捉拿歸案了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饒命啊 殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要罰就罰我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請一定要對孩子們從輕處罰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大膽 就因為這幫傢夥 讓殿下陷入危機之中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 放開他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 這怎麼能交代..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的話就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝您的大恩大德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.51,0:19:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我長大之後一定會加入騎兵隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任由殿下差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要平安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會回來救你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去備馬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和王宮裡教的不一樣 好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想跟其他被囚禁的魯西達尼亞人聊聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 趕緊搬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點搬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您萬萬不可來這種骯髒的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把他們殺了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於鬧得沒辦法所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯西達尼亞人跟野獸沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馴是馴不服的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 動作快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人 要是乖乖成為奴隸的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就不用死了啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等哪天殿下即位之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有位友人想請殿下錄用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那個人 說不定能回答殿下的疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 糟糕..說漏嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.81,0:21:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於那傢夥性格乖僻 您就當我什麼都沒說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 吊人胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看再過幾十年 父王的王位都不會動搖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即位之事 我還想都沒法想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有父王在 我帕爾斯定然安泰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的那位友人 似乎暫時無緣相見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.74,0:22:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 三年之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王都葉克巴達那被烈焰和血霧包圍..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於魯西達尼亞的侵略
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:30.31,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(393,61)}{\fad(1200,800)}馬爾亞姆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:30.31,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(726,536)}{\fad(1200,800)}帕爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盟國 馬爾亞姆王國滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.27,0:22:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的進攻終於波及到帕爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕爾斯歷320年 秋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王太子亞爾斯蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.76,0:22:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時年14歲 初陣在即
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.42,0:24:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風去風來 迷霧飄散
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞爾斯蘭以為那是吉兆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 十四歲、初陣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.11,0:24:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年 即將成王
